                    <i class="icon icon-office-44 icon-active"></i>
                    <span class="h7">Increase Sales</span>

                    <p class="thin">Beeketing can help you increase 20%-75% revenue. </p>
                </article>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-6 col-xs-12">
                <article class="center">
                    <i class="icon icon-shopping-18 icon-active"></i>
                    <span class="h7">Happy Customers</span>

                    <p class="thin">We help you send .</p>
